children.text:
# **Gleason Score for Prostate Cancer**

Prognoses prostate cancer based on microscopic tumor appearance. It is the standard staging criteria for prostate cancer

children.label: Primary grade
children.name: primary_grade

options.text: Recognizable glands, but cells are darker.

children.helpertext: The dominant pattern of the tumor (>50% of total pattern seen)

children.label: Secondary grade
children.name: secondary_grade

options.text: Recognizable glands, but cells are darker.

children.helpertext: The highest grade pattern seen after the primary pattern

children.label: Tertiary grade
children.name: tertiary_grade

options.text: Recognizable glands, but cells are darker.

children.helpertext: Small component of a third (generally more aggressive) pattern
